<H1>&nbsp;</H1>
<H1>Weighted Petri Nets</H1>
</CENTER>

<UL><UL><UL> <UL><UL><UL>
  <LI><FONT size=5>Generalized the original Petri net to allow 
            <FONT color=mediumblue>multiple tokens</FONT>         to be
added/removed when a transition fires</FONT>
  <LI><FONT size=5>The edges 
            are labeled with the <FONT color=mediumblue>weight</FONT>       (i.e., number of tokens)</FONT>
  <LI><FONT size=5>If there 
            is no label, then the <FONT color=mediumblue>default value is 
            1</FONT>          </FONT></LI>
</UL></UL></UL></UL></UL></UL>

